         <div xml:id="alalal-e76204"><!-- l3d22a11 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-e76204-Hd1e99">Articulus 11</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-e76204-Hd1e101" type="question-title">Corrigia calceamenti et ossa regis 
Idumee quid significent ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e76204-d1e104">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="63"/>ARTICULUS XI.
<lb ed="Bd" n="64"/>Corrigia calceamenti et ossa regis 
Idu<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="65"/>mee quid significent ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e76204-d1e113">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="66"/>Deinde quaeritur de ultimo verbo quod
<lb ed="Bd" n="67"/>dicit Magister quasi per modum epilogi,
<lb ed="Bd" n="68"/>ibi, D, ยง 2: <quote xml:id="alalal-e76204-Qd1e121"> Haec de corrigia 
calcea<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="69"/>ment, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e76204-d1e127">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="70"/>Quid enim hic dicatur corrigia ? quid
<lb ed="Bd" n="71"/>caleeamentum ? quid rex Idumee ? et,
<lb ed="Bd" n="72"/>Que ossa egus ? et, Quomodo 
incendun<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="73"/>tur usque ad cineres ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e76204-d1e139">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="74"/>Solutio Dicendum, quod calceeamen-
<pb ed="#Bd" n="402"/>
               <cb ed="#Bd" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="1"/>tum est humanitas regens pedem 
divi<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="2"/>nitatis, qui solus sians, omnia sustentat
<lb ed="Bd" n="3"/>sacco hujus morticine et animalis pellis.
<lb ed="Bd" n="4"/>Corrigta autem ligans, est unio duarum
<lb ed="Bd" n="5"/>naturarum in singularitatem persone.
<lb ed="Bd" n="6"/>fex autem Idumez, Christus rex mundi
<lb ed="Bd" n="7"/>per conformitatem sanguinis: quia carni
<lb ed="Bd" n="8"/>et sanguini communicavit. Et Idumza
<lb ed="Bd" n="9"/>sanguinea interpretatur, sicut Psalmista
<cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="10"/>dicit: In Idumaeam extendam 
calcea<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="11"/>mentum meum'. Ossa autem sunt ea
<lb ed="Bd" n="12"/>que fortiora sunt ad intelligendum inter
<lb ed="Bd" n="13"/>sacramenta humanitatis ejus. Ad 
cine<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="14"/>rem autem incendi, est igne fervoris 
stu<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="15"/>dii per rationes usque ad minima velle
<lb ed="Bd" n="16"/>investigare. Et hoc non est faciendum,
<lb ed="Bd" n="17"/>ut dicit Magister.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e76204-d1e187">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="18"/>Et sic patet distinctio XXII.
</p>
